KATE:
Bye!

01:47.475 --> 01:48.642
Bye.

01:48.676 --> 01:50.211
Aww.

01:51.779 --> 01:53.547
Bye sweetheart.

01:53.847 --> 01:54.815
GIRL:
Do I get a fist bump?

01:54.848 --> 01:56.384
WOMAN:
Nice.

01:57.418 --> 01:58.186
High five?

01:58.219 --> 01:59.753
Awesome.

01:59.953 --> 02:01.189
GIRL:
I'll miss you,
Miss Carter.

02:01.222 --> 02:02.323
KATE:
Aw, I'll miss you too.

02:02.356 --> 02:03.224
Bye.

02:03.257 --> 02:05.193
GIRL:
Bye!

02:05.659 --> 02:06.627
(door squeaks)

02:06.660 --> 02:07.495
(door closes)

02:07.528 --> 02:08.762
ALLAN:
Well that's
the last of 'em.

02:08.795 --> 02:11.599
You know what time it is now?

02:11.632 --> 02:12.433
It's party time.

02:12.466 --> 02:14.368
* It's party time,
party time, *

02:14.402 --> 02:16.804
* it's party time in the
teacher's lounge! *

02:20.674 --> 02:22.543
KATE:
Well I really miss you.

02:22.576 --> 02:24.878
BRAD:
Me too.

02:24.912 --> 02:28.716
KATE:
I...I'm really glad you
had time to talk,

02:28.749 --> 02:30.518
I just wish you could have
come out here,

02:30.551 --> 02:32.586
you know, it's so beautiful.

02:32.620 --> 02:34.888
BRAD:
I wish I could have
made it work with my schedule.

02:34.922 --> 02:36.590
Say, isn't there a
going away party being thrown

02:36.624 --> 02:37.891
in your honour?

02:37.925 --> 02:39.159
KATE:
Yeah.

02:39.193 --> 02:44.632
I mean I could go to the party
or I could stay here with you.

02:45.533 --> 02:47.835
BRAD:
Kate, anybody could walk in.

02:47.868 --> 02:48.636
KATE:
I know.

02:48.669 --> 02:50.804
You know, we could...

02:51.739 --> 02:53.741
BRAD:
(coughing)

02:53.774 --> 02:55.108
KATE:
Are you okay?

02:55.142 --> 02:59.547
BRAD:
Yeah, that's why I always
keep an emergency water handy.

03:00.414 --> 03:01.449
KATE:
Heh.

03:04.285 --> 03:06.520
BRAD:
I love you One-Week-From-Now-
Mrs-Cholowski.

03:06.554 --> 03:07.888
KATE:
Aww, I love you too,

03:07.921 --> 03:11.625
Current-And-Forever-
Mr-Cholowski.

03:11.659 --> 03:12.460
(laughing)

03:12.493 --> 03:13.427
BRAD:
I should go.

03:13.461 --> 03:14.628
Enjoy your party.

03:14.662 --> 03:15.996
KATE:
Okay.

03:16.029 --> 03:18.432
I'll see you soon, honey.

03:19.400 --> 03:20.534
Bye.

03:23.937 --> 03:27.641
