to think of me as Joe.

03:59.673 --> 04:01.942
KATE:
Okay.

04:01.975 --> 04:04.645
JOE:
And I know you have
an interest in literature,

04:04.678 --> 04:07.615
you know, and back at mine
I have some first editions

04:07.648 --> 04:10.017
that I would love to show you.

04:10.050 --> 04:14.622
KATE:
Uh, well I'm sure
your first editions are um,

04:14.655 --> 04:16.023
impressive...

04:16.055 --> 04:20.327
you know have my own
waiting for me back home.

04:20.361 --> 04:21.762
So...

04:21.795 --> 04:23.864
ALLAN:
Joe you sly fox,
you hitting on Miss Katie again?

04:23.897 --> 04:28.001
JOE:
Uh, yes, yes I was, but I
had a better line this time.

04:28.035 --> 04:30.538
I've been working on it,
and oh, I'm being

04:30.571 --> 04:33.374
dragged away now, yeah, okay.

04:33.407 --> 04:34.475
KATE:
(laughing)

04:34.508 --> 04:35.343
Thank you.

04:35.376 --> 04:36.344
ALLAN:
Sorry.

04:36.377 --> 04:38.546
I have no idea how to
explain what that was.

04:38.579 --> 04:40.814
KATE:
It's...it's okay,
I'm used to it by now,

04:40.848 --> 04:44.618
and to be fair, he did put a
little bit more effort into it;

04:44.652 --> 04:45.953
this time it wasn't all
just smiling and,

04:45.986 --> 04:48.021
you know, bumping
against me, so.

04:48.055 --> 04:49.423
ALLAN:
Yes, he is getting better.

04:49.457 --> 04:50.324
KATE:
Yeah.

04:50.358 --> 04:51.592
ALLAN:
As we all are,
thanks to you.

04:51.625 --> 04:52.760
KATE:
Aw, you're sweet.

04:52.793 --> 04:54.495
ALLAN:
I gotta go do something.

04:54.528 --> 04:56.330
WOMAN:
Now, come this way.

04:56.364 --> 04:58.065
KATE:
Oh...

05:00.734 --> 05:02.603
ALLAN:
Excuse me, everyone?

05:02.636 --> 05:06.874
As we all know, tonight
is our last night with Kate.

05:06.907 --> 05:08.776
She's leaving us
tomorrow morning,

05:08.809 --> 05:10.911
back to civilization,
and to her family,

05:10.944 --> 05:12.780
and to get married.

05:12.813 --> 05:16.016
We wanna thank you for
coming up all the way to our

05:16.049 --> 05:18.419
little community
and giving of yourself.

05:18.452 --> 05:20.821
It takes a special person to
come up here and live

05:20.854 --> 05:23.957
and work with us out of the
goodness of their heart.

05:23.991 --> 05:24.825
(sighs)

05:24.858 --> 05:26.093
'Cause we know
it's not for the money.

05:26.126 --> 05:28.429
KATE:
(chuckles)

05:28.462 --> 05:31.799
ALLAN:
It's not for everyone,
but you fit right in,

05:31.832 --> 05:34.568
and we really wish we could
talk you into coming back to us.

05:34.602 --> 05:36.637
JOE:
Me too.

05:37.638 --> 05:40.474
ALLAN:
Kate, although
it's only been a short time,

05:40.508 --> 05:42.776
we will miss you.

05:42.810 --> 05:47.615
We love you, and you will
always be a part of our family.

