10:06.740 --> 10:10.678
REDFORD:
Do you see
a runway out there?

10:10.911 --> 10:13.113
KATE:
Uh, nope.

10:13.146 --> 10:15.015
REDFORD:
Because it's under
three feet of snow.

10:15.048 --> 10:17.284
They can't land the plane
or take off without a runway,

10:17.317 --> 10:18.686
hence, no pilots.

10:18.719 --> 10:23.190
KATE:
Okay, but I, I have a ticket
for a flight that leaves today,

10:23.223 --> 10:25.425
