10:25.458 --> 10:27.060
REDFORD:
Yeah, so do I.

10:28.829 --> 10:32.766
KATE:
Uh, I...I'm getting married
in a couple of days,

10:32.800 --> 10:34.301
in Snowy Pines.

10:34.334 --> 10:37.237
REDFORD:
Hah.

10:37.270 --> 10:38.906
