10:56.023 --> 10:56.824
REDFORD:
Ow!

10:56.857 --> 10:58.425
Ah!

10:59.159 --> 11:00.193
KATE:
I'm sorry.

11:00.227 --> 11:02.029
I'm sorry, I'm sorry,
I'm sorry.

11:02.062 --> 11:03.964
You, you were just
gonna leave me here,

11:03.997 --> 11:05.933
you can't just leave me here.

11:05.966 --> 11:07.467
REDFORD:
Who throws a candle?

11:07.500 --> 11:09.369
KATE:
I just really need
to get to Snowy Pines.

11:09.402 --> 11:10.871
REDFORD:
Lady, I mind my own business.

11:10.904 --> 11:13.206
KATE:
Okay, well so do I,
but sometimes,

11:13.240 --> 11:14.474
I like to help people.

11:14.507 --> 11:15.408
REDFORD:
Lady.

11:15.442 --> 11:16.476
KATE:
Okay.

11:16.509 --> 11:19.880
When do you think the
runways are gonna be open.

11:19.913 --> 11:20.981
REDFORD:
A week.

11:21.014 --> 11:21.849
KATE:
A week.

11:21.882 --> 11:23.350
