I don't have 72 hours,

11:28.321 --> 11:31.158
so what am I
supposed to do here?

11:31.424 --> 11:33.727
Are you, are you
going on this thing?

11:33.761 --> 11:34.962
Will you take me with you?

11:34.995 --> 11:36.730
