12:44.932 --> 12:47.067
CINDY:
Pastor dude told me
I can't stick anything

12:47.100 --> 12:49.169
on that Holy guy.

12:49.202 --> 12:51.271
I don't know what to
do with all that stuff.

12:51.304 --> 12:53.573
EDWARD:
Diane, why is he
not cooperating with us,

12:53.606 --> 12:56.009
this was supposed to be
a done deal,

12:56.043 --> 12:58.411
gah, when is Kate
gonna be here?

12:58.445 --> 13:00.848
CINDY:
Brad went to pick her up
at the airport.

13:00.881 --> 13:02.983
EDWARD:
Well, I should hope so.

13:03.016 --> 13:06.319
Because I am tired of
all this falling on to me.

13:06.353 --> 13:09.222
You know,
'cause I don't need this.

13:09.256 --> 13:12.059
I'm married already,
am I not married already?

13:12.092 --> 13:13.593
DIANE:
Are you giving me
a choice, dear?

13:13.626 --> 13:15.295
EDWARD:
That is not funny,
do not say that,

13:15.328 --> 13:17.497
none of you are funny.

13:17.530 --> 13:19.599
Nobody listens to me,
you're all against me,

13:19.632 --> 13:21.034
and I don't know why--.

13:21.068 --> 13:22.135
Brad, Brad!

13:22.169 --> 13:23.570
Where's Kate?

13:23.603 --> 13:25.906
BRAD:
Everything's fine,
she's just gonna be

13:25.939 --> 13:27.240
