53:23.268 --> 53:27.872
Don't worry,
you'll be next.

53:27.905 --> 53:30.308
KATE:
Uh, yeah, you wish.

53:30.341 --> 53:32.677
REDFORD:
You ain't got nothin'
I haven't seen before.

53:32.710 --> 53:34.945
KATE:
How do you know
what I have and haven't got?

53:34.979 --> 53:39.684
REDFORD:
Basic anatomy.

53:40.818 --> 53:45.790
You should probably allow
an inch or so for shrinkage,

53:45.823 --> 53:46.724
probably two.

53:46.757 --> 53:48.493
KATE:
Oh.

53:48.526 --> 53:50.295
