57:09.494 --> 57:12.530
KATE:
Ugh.

57:15.900 --> 57:16.667
REDFORD:
Ah.

57:16.701 --> 57:18.736
KATE:
Wait wait wait wait wait.

57:18.769 --> 57:21.939
REDFORD:
What?

57:24.141 --> 57:26.076
What, come on lady,
it's freezing out here!

57:26.110 --> 57:28.012
KATE:
Okay, can you stop it,
with the 'lady' thing?

57:28.045 --> 57:29.947
I know you're
trying to be a big man,

57:29.980 --> 57:34.652
