it's a little demeaning, just...

57:34.685 --> 57:37.988
come back, okay?

57:38.022 --> 57:39.824
REDFORD:
Yeah well if I don't
get food or more clothes,

57:39.857 --> 57:42.560
I might as well
not come back, so.

57:42.993 --> 57:44.595
KATE:
Okay, well, give 'er.

57:44.629 --> 57:46.230
REDFORD:
Thanks.

57:47.998 --> 57:50.668
(splash)

57:56.974 --> 58:05.550
