58:18.896 --> 58:21.031
KATE:
What do you think Jodi
would say about that?

58:21.065 --> 58:24.902
REDFORD:
I'm sure she'd say
'better you than me.'

58:26.136 --> 58:30.007
KATE:
Well she sounds
